# Cherry-101 Commit Checklist:
# [ ] Self-review of code changes
# [ ] Tests pass locally
# [ ] Documentation updated (if needed)
# [ ] No new warnings or errors
# [ ] Follows CherryScript coding conventions
# [ ] Version compatibility checked
# [ ] Dependencies updated (if needed)
# ===============================================

# ===============================================
# Special Notes for Cherry-101:
# - Remember: Cherry-101 is the FIRST CherryScript program
# - Maintain backward compatibility when possible
# - Include practical examples for new features
# - Update test.cherry-101 for major changes
# - Keep the spirit of "A sweet way to code"
